---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Responsible AI | HeatherAI"
  description="HeatherAI handles sensitive health data, personal goals, and emotional moments. Here's how we build responsibly, with guardrails, transparency, and privacy by design."
>

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 md:px-12 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block text-[11px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[3px] font-semibold mb-4">
      Responsible AI
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 max-w-[900px] mx-auto leading-[1.05]">
      Built to coach.<br />
      <em class="not-italic text-accent">Built with guardrails.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/50 max-w-[680px] mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      HeatherAI handles sensitive health data, personal goals, and emotional moments.
      We take that seriously. Here's how we build responsibly.
    </p>
  </section>


  <!-- ============ PILLARS ============ -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/[0.06]">
    <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto">

      <div class="space-y-6">

        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Domain-Scoped AI</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            HeatherAI only coaches nutrition and behavior change. It doesn't diagnose medical
            conditions, prescribe medications, or provide therapy. The AI has explicit boundaries.
            When a conversation moves outside its domain, it says so and defers to qualified professionals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Expert-in-the-Loop</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            Every response is grounded in Heather Bauer's methodology, not generated from generic
            internet content. The AI operates within coaching frameworks developed by a credentialed
            registered dietitian over a full career of practice. It doesn't freelance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Medical Safety Boundaries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            When users mention medical conditions, medications, or clinical symptoms, HeatherAI
            recognizes the boundary and defers. "Talk to your doctor" isn't a disclaimer: it's
            built into the coaching logic. A dedicated
            <a href="/pricing" class="text-accent hover:underline">human-coach tier</a> is
            waitlist-only, for situations that call for deeper clinical judgment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Data Privacy &amp; De-identification</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            HeatherAI was developed using Heather's coaching methodology: the frameworks and
            approaches she's refined over a 25-year practice. Any historical coaching material
            used in building the AI has been fully de-identified, with all names, phone numbers, and
            other personal information removed before any analysis. Your conversations and health
            data with HeatherAI are encrypted in transit and at rest, are never sold, and are
            never used to train third-party AI models.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Transparent AI Identity</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            HeatherAI is always identified as AI. It never pretends to be a human. The coaching
            voice is modeled on Heather Bauer's methodology, but every interaction is clearly an
            AI-generated response, not a direct communication from Heather herself.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">What's Ahead</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            We hold ourselves to clinical-grade standards for privacy and safety: encryption in
            transit and at rest, de-identification of coaching material, expert review of real
            sessions, and immediate escalation of medical concerns to a registered dietitian.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ============ PRIVACY PROMISE ============ -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/[0.06]">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-accent/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[3px] font-semibold mb-3 text-center">
          Privacy Promise
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-center">
          De-identified. Encrypted. <em class="not-italic text-accent">Never sold.</em>
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span>Any historical coaching material used in building HeatherAI has been fully de-identified: no names, phone numbers, or personal information.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span>Your conversations with HeatherAI are encrypted in transit and at rest.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span>We never sell user data. We never train third-party AI models on your data.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span>Held to clinical-grade standards for privacy and safety, with expert review of real sessions.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-[13px] text-accent hover:underline">Read the full privacy policy &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
